mondays at &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 2012 short documentary film directed by cynthia wade , about two sisters who open their long island hair salon to women diagnosed with cancer , every third monday of the month . the film was nominated for the 2013 academy award for best documentary ( short subject ) . after being nominated for an academy award the film was released along with all the other 15 oscar-nominated short films in theaters by shortshd .